{"tid":1616362,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星、Sony 停止在中國生產手機   中國廠房將完全關閉","createTime":"2019-10-03T11:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:59:04.000Z","uid":109923,"like":201,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a4aad93e28445fa4ac005daa177679594b1c88","tid":1616362,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"隨著中美貿易戰越演越烈，全球的生產鏈發生重大變化，再加上人工成本上升等因素，不少知名品牌把生產線撤出中國。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三星公司在本週三宣布，關閉位於中國惠州的最後一家智能手機工廠。</span><br />\n<br />\n消息指由於近年中國勞動成本提高，再加上經濟放緩，三星在週三發表公告，正式關閉「惠州工廠」即該品牌在中國最後一個手機工廠，把生產線全面移到印度和越南等生產成本較低國家，從以減低生產成本。公告中表示：「基於市場需求的全球生產戰略，惠州工場的生產設備將轉移至全球其他國家的生產地」。根據市場調查公司 Counterpoint 數據指，三星在中國市場的佔有率從 2013 年的 15％ 下降至 2019 年首季的 1％。<br />\n<br />\n撤出中國生產線的或不只有三星，有報道指 Sony 將關閉位於北京智能手機工廠，轉移到泰國繼續生產。除了工資節節上漲、手機產品不敵當地本土品牌外，中美貿易戰更是加速工廠撤離中國的原因之一。"},{"pid":"f1179f115cbb1ed54bfd7cedab23003eb26dc0de","tid":1616362,"uid":85552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db4da78bea9bdfe9781e089e46cef9f22f14dd7","tid":1616362,"uid":63164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631557a02a6ad4e08e40db2a200d6ab98609d5b4","tid":1616362,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263eec231affd9eb5c94af32fc9345ad73a